 Technical launch problems solved. Now that governments and the crooked insider trading, graft, &amp; collusion of governmental contractors is removed from launch operations, costs to orbit come down to a fraction of the bad old days. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#6F6F6F>- </font><a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/bnuclearspace>NuclearSpace Message Board</a><font color=#6F6F6F> - </font><a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm1>Open Forum</a> <font color=#6F6F6F> - </font><a href="http://www.nuclearspace.com">NuclearSpace Home Page</a><font color=#6F6F6F> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.245<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

